7. Top 10 critical findings with remediation steps
8. Full findings appendix

## Output Files

| File | Description |
|---|---|
| `iac-policy/checkov-results.json` | Raw Checkov JSON output |
| `iac-policy/opa-results.json` | OPA policy evaluation results |
| `iac-policy/sbom/filesystem-sbom.spdx.json` | SPDX SBOM |
| `iac-policy/sbom/filesystem-sbom.cdx.json` | CycloneDX SBOM |
| `iac-policy/compliance-map.json` | Control-by-control compliance status |
| `iac-policy/iac-report.md` | Full security report |

## Error Handling

| Situation | Action |
|---|---|
| No IaC files found | Report "No IaC files detected" and exit cleanly |
| Checkov parse error on a file | Log the file, skip it, continue scanning |
| Syft unavailable | Skip SBOM phase, note in report |
